title: 12/30/20 – DPS – Best Of
itunes:title: 12/30/20 – DPS – Best Of
description:
LaVar Arrington and T.J. Houshmandzadeh fill in for Dan Patrick and break down Dwayne Haskins’ downward spiral since entering the league last season. The guys question if the former Ohio State product can salvage his career with a new franchise. They discuss J.J. Watt’s emphatic speech to the media and speak with Hall of Fame quarterback and Heisman Trophy winner Danny Wuerffel. Plus, the third member of 'Up On Game', Plaxico Burress, joins the show!
